    "description": {
      "description": "<p>Mira, Projétil</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Saca a arma e atira com movimentos ligeiros e imprevisíveis.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Condição:</span> ter pistola ou outra arma balística de uma mão para saque.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Esforço:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 4.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Dano:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> </span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">+4</span><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family:'MS Mincho';mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">Ⓐ</span>.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Efeitos:</span> ao declarar a ação tem Iniciativa +4 na rodada. Ignora as penalidades por estar Engajado.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Pré-requisitos:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> Balística N5.</span></p>",
